variables.name: prompt-assignment
variables.description: A variable you can use for assignments

defaultValue.string:
Please complete the following information on form LE-10:

1.       Account No. – Enter your Illinois unemployment account number

2.       Employer – Enter your business’s legal name

3.       Located At – Enter your business’s street address, city, state, and zip code

4.       Telephone Number – Enter your business’s telephone number

5.       Email Address – Enter your company’s contact email address         

6.       Signature – Have the person noted under Name of Employer sign the form

7.       Name of Employer – Enter your business’s legal name

8.       By – Enter person’s name signing the form, should be an officer of the company

9.       Title – Enter the title of the person signing the form

10.     Date – Enter the date the form is signed

Thank you
